org.purl.co.interfaces
Interface COList<E>

All Superinterfaces:
COBag<E>, COCollection<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
StandardCOList
public interface COList<E>
extends COBag<E>

This interface represents a CO list as a specialisation of a CO bag, i.e., a CO collection with order and repetition.

Author:
Paolo Ciccarese, Silvio Peroni

add

boolean add(java.net.URI coitemuri,
            int index,
            E o)
This method adds a new object to the list, that will be dereferenced through a new CO list item created starting from the URI specified as input.

Parameters:
coitemuri - the URI of the list item dereferencing the object of the list.
index - the position in which adding the list item.
o - the object to add.
Returns:
true if the object it is correctly added, false otherwise.
